Description: Cyviz AS is a Norway-based global technology provider for comprehensive conference rooms, control rooms and experience centers. The Company develops, markets, sells and installs software and hardware visualization solutions for all types of meeting rooms based on a self-developed IT platform for collaboration, management and control of the meeting rooms in various organizations, including participating in other companies with similar activities. The Company serves global enterprises and governments. The Company has 100% ownership in subsidiaries: Cyviz LLC (USA), Cyviz Limited (United Kingdom), Cyviz Pty Ltd (Australia) and Cyviz Pte Ltd (Singapore). The Company operates in Norway, United Kingdom, United States, United Arab Emirates, Singapore, Saudi Arabia and Indonesia.
